#TDD Testing Kata
Practice rspec test writing & solutions to pass quizes.


Examples borrowed from http://www.codequizzes.com/


1) Write test for a "word_count" method that will return number of words in a given string.

2) Write test for a "average_word_length" method that will return the average length of string of words.

3) Write test for a "palindrome?" method that will test if a giving word is palindrome.
